JOHANNESBURG &#8211; A memorial service will be held for gospel singer Lundi Tyamara at the Grace Bible Church in Soweto on Tuesday.Tyamara passed away on Friday at the age of 38 after a long battle with abdominal tuberculosis and liver complications.His manager says his family, friends and fans will gather to celebrate his life.Tyamara will be laid to rest on Sunday in his home town of Worcester in the Western Cape.